Class StagedSuite.SuiteEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.EventObject
      • com.itko.lisa.testing.StagedSuite.SuiteEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    StagedSuite

    public static class StagedSuite.SuiteEvent
extends java.util.EventObject
    The class that hold suite-level event info. If you add yourself to the event sink for just this StagedSuite (not its sub-tests), you'll get back on your listener objects of this class. The event ID returned will be one of the TestEvent.EVENT_SUITE* events The event source (as in the EventObject.getSource()) is either of type RegressionRunner or StagedSuite. The event ID drives which
    See Also:
    TestEvent, RegressionRunner, Serialized Form
